利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 为“Definitely Maybe” 30 周年纪念巡演增加额外日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-adds-extra-dates-to-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3518617?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=liam-加拉格尔为 30 周年纪念巡演购买门票添加了额外日期Liberty DunworthFri, 20 Oct 2023 09:53:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3518617 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新日期为伦敦和曼彻斯特</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-adds-extra-dates-to-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3518617">Liam Gallagher 为“Definitely Maybe”30 周年纪念巡演添加额外日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>为他的 2024 年“绝对可能”巡演添加了更多日期。请在下面查看门票详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/liam-gallagher-oasis-reunion-tour-noel-interview-2020-new-album-2615869"><em>NME</em>大读物 – Liam Gallagher：“绿洲团聚很快就会发生”</a></strong></li></ul><p>正如本周早些时候宣布的那样，这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>主唱将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">明年夏天开始英国和爱尔兰巡演</a>，以庆祝该乐队 1994 年首张专辑发行 30 周年。</p><p>巡演门票于今天上午 9 点（10 月 20 日）开始发售，由于需求量很大，加拉格尔现在宣布了两个额外的日期。</p><p>其中包括 6 月 11 日在伦敦 O2 体育馆举行的第四次约会，以及 6 月 28 日在这位歌手的家乡曼彻斯特在 Co-Op Live 举行的一场额外演出。</p><p>之前列出的日期包括谢菲尔德、卡迪夫、格拉斯哥和都柏林的竞技场。所有门票现已发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fliam-gallagher-tickets%2Fartist%2F2055477" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到。</p><p>这些现场表演是这位歌手今年早些时候分享的更新的后续，他在更新中回顾了这一里程碑，并戏弄歌迷说他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-next-year-for-30th-anniversary-3442321">正在寻找完整播放 1994 年专辑的方法。</a></p><p>利亚姆继续调侃这个前景，后来宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-promises-naughty-oasis-b-sides-on-definitely-maybe-tour-including-the-noel-sung-half-the-world-away-3513284">他也会演奏那个时代的“顽皮”B面歌曲</a>以及由他的兄弟、前乐队成员和绿洲乐队首席词曲作者诺埃尔演唱的《半个世界》。 </p><figure id="attachment_3518621" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3518621" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3518621" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="利亚姆·加拉格尔表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Gallagher-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3518621" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·加拉格尔表演。图片来源：黛比·希基/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>“我在房子里跳来跳去，宣布‘绝对可能’巡演，”他当时说道。 “90 年代最重要的专辑没有之一。没有它我就不会在任何地方，你也不会，所以让我们一起庆祝 LG x”</p><p>在他的独奏项目和之前的癌症恐慌之后，前 Oasis 吉他手 Bonehead 似乎也将加入他的巡演—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/oasis-bonehead-on-recent-cancer-diagnosis-its-all-clear-its-gone-3320076">此后他的病情已经解除</a>。然而，昨天（10 月 19 日）这位歌手表示，兄弟兼前乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-gallagher-turned-down-definitely-maybe-tour-3516455">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 拒绝了参加即将举行的约会的邀请。</a></p><p>尽管没有参加巡演，诺埃尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-for-2024-denies-oasis-reunion-tour-3436441">确实确认了在 30 周年纪念日重新发行这张影响深远的专辑以纪念这一时刻的计划</a>。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">作为 In Conversation 系列的一部分，诺埃尔在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>表示，“从来没有真正认真地提出过关于‘The Big O’复合的提议”。</p><p>在利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 的其他新闻中，这位英伦流行偶像最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-live-in-knebworth-kasabian-amyl-sniffers-3239799">在 2022 年纳贝沃斯 (Knebworth) 演出中</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-announces-knebworth-live-album-and-shares-roll-it-over-video-watch-footage-preorder-3454697">发布了一张现场专辑</a>。这次活动是他作为独奏艺术家迄今为止规模最大的头条演出之一，两个晚上他的演奏吸引了超过 170,000 名观众。</p><p>他还开玩笑说，他的新个人专辑——2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-cmon-you-know-3231721">《C&#39;Mon You Know》</a>的后续专辑——<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-hints-that-his-new-album-is-done-3499289">现已完成</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-adds-extra-dates-to-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3518617">Liam Gallagher 为“Definitely Maybe”30 周年纪念巡演添加额外日期的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
